  Lines:
  - SpeakerName: Hecatina
    SpeakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    Text: My Lord! You've awakened... The ritual was... intense. But there is no
      time for rest.
    PortraitOnLeft: 0
    EventID: 
  - SpeakerName: Hecatina
    SpeakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    Text: Lesser shadows have breached the outer corridor. They sense your weakened
      state.
    PortraitOnLeft: 0
    EventID: 
  - SpeakerName: Hecatina
    SpeakerPortrait: {fileID: 0}
    Text: You are still recovering, but you can still guide your vassals. Send Ignis
      forth to hold the line.
